housefull 3 is a 2016 indian comedy film co-written and directed by sajid-farhad . it is the third installment in the housefull film series . produced by sajid nadiadwala under his banner nadiadwala grandson entertainment , it is distributed by eros international . housefull 3 features akshay kumar , abhishek bachchan , riteish deshmukh , jacqueline fernandez , nargis fakhri , and lisa haydon in the lead roles . principal photography began in october 2015 with filming locations including london and delhi . the film released on 3 june 2016 .